Day 1 (1.5 hr)

HTML structure: <!DOCTYPE>, <html>, <head>, <body>

Basic tags: headings, paragraphs, links, images

Hands-on: Create a simple page with headings, paragraphs, and images

Day 2 (1.5 hr)

Lists: ordered <ol>, unordered <ul>, definition <dl>

Tables: <table>, <tr>, <td>, <th>

Hands-on: Build a simple table of students or products

Day 3 (1.5 hr)

Forms: <form>, <input>, <textarea>, <select>, <button>

Form attributes: name, id, placeholder, required

Hands-on: Create a basic registration form

Day 4 (1.5 hr)

HTML semantic elements: <header>, <footer>, <section>, <article>

Accessibility basics: alt, aria-label

Hands-on: Rebuild previous form with semantic HTML

Day 5 (1.5 hr)

HTML5 features: audio, video, iframe, canvas

Hands-on: Embed a video and map iframe

Day 6 (1.5 hr)

HTML attributes deep dive: class, id, title, data-*

Meta tags: charset, viewport, SEO basics

Hands-on: Create a basic HTML page with meta tags

Day 7 (2 hr)

Mini project: Personal portfolio page (HTML only)

Features: Header, about section, image, contact form

Week 2: CSS Fundamentals

Day 8 (1.5 hr)

CSS syntax & selectors: element, class, id, universal

Inline, internal, external CSS

Hands-on: Style headings, paragraphs, links on portfolio page

Day 9 (1.5 hr)

Colors: named, HEX, RGB, HSL

Typography: font-family, font-size, font-weight, text-align, line-height

Hands-on: Style your portfolio text

Day 10 (1.5 hr)

Box model: margin, border, padding, width, height

Hands-on: Add spacing & borders to portfolio sections

Day 11 (1.5 hr)

Backgrounds: color, image, position, repeat, size

Hands-on: Add background images or colors to header/footer

Day 12 (1.5 hr)

Display & visibility: block, inline, inline-block, none

Positioning: static, relative, absolute, fixed, sticky

Hands-on: Position a header/footer on portfolio page

Day 13 (1.5 hr)

Flexbox basics: display: flex, justify-content, align-items, flex-wrap

Hands-on: Make a responsive navigation bar

Day 14 (2 hr)

Mini project: Portfolio page with CSS

Add layout with flexbox, styling, colors, spacing

Week 3: Intermediate CSS & Layouts

Day 15 (1.5 hr)

CSS Grid basics: display: grid, grid-template-columns/rows

Hands-on: Create a 2-column layout for portfolio

Day 16 (1.5 hr)

Pseudo-classes: :hover, :focus, :nth-child

Pseudo-elements: ::before, ::after

Hands-on: Add hover effects to buttons & links

Day 17 (1.5 hr)

CSS transitions & animations: transition, transform, keyframes

Hands-on: Animate a button or image

Day 18 (1.5 hr)

Responsive design basics: @media queries, viewport units

Hands-on: Make portfolio responsive for mobile

Day 19 (1.5 hr)

CSS units: px, em, rem, %, vh, vw

Hands-on: Adjust spacing & font sizes using relative units

Day 20 (1.5 hr)

Advanced selectors: attribute selectors, combinators

Hands-on: Style form elements with advanced selectors

Day 21 (2 hr)

Mini project: Responsive portfolio page

Flexbox, Grid, hover effects, media queries

Week 4: Advanced CSS & Interview Prep

Day 22 (1.5 hr)

CSS variables (custom properties)

Hands-on: Use variables for colors & fonts

Day 23 (1.5 hr)

CSS specificity & inheritance

Hands-on: Solve conflicting styles in mini project

Day 24 (1.5 hr)

Positioning tricks: sticky nav, overlapping sections

Hands-on: Add sticky navigation in portfolio

Day 25 (1.5 hr)

CSS frameworks overview: Bootstrap / Tailwind

Hands-on: Convert one section of portfolio to Tailwind

Day 26 (1.5 hr)

Common layout patterns: cards, grids, hero sections

