Day 27 (1.5 hr)

Debugging & browser tools: Chrome DevTools

Hands-on: Inspect and fix CSS issues in your page

Day 28 (1.5 hr)

CSS best practices: BEM, naming conventions, DRY

Hands-on: Refactor portfolio CSS

Day 29 (1.5 hr)

Mini project: Complete portfolio with advanced CSS

