Day 30 (2 hr)

Full revision:

Go through HTML & CSS concepts

Practice interview questions: semantic HTML, box model, flex/grid, responsive layouts

Final check on portfolio project

✅ Tips:

Practice small mini-projects daily (buttons, cards, forms)

Use DevTools for debugging CSS

Keep portfolio page evolving every week